    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/60d86fb9aa2fc2293a7d9e00669c7039.poster.avif?t=1771047675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/60d86fb9aa2fc2293a7d9e00669c7039.webm?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/60d86fb9aa2fc2293a7d9e00669c7039.mp4?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>罗波弗伦兹 是一个沙盒式的首领战斗游戏，在此您可以制作武器和建造机器，与受到日常电子产品启发的巨大机器人战斗。<br><br>用您制造的剑砸碎一台发怒的电视，或巧妙地建造一个带电的陷阱来粉碎一台暴躁的计算机。击败机器人首领后，带着新材料回到欧米兰建设您的城镇。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制造武器</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/be7691f20fba86bfffc812a08637bf01.poster.avif?t=1771047675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/be7691f20fba86bfffc812a08637bf01.webm?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/be7691f20fba86bfffc812a08637bf01.mp4?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>欧米兰 曾是一个模范城市，巨大的机械照顾着人们...直到有人在控制所有巨大机器的服务器上洒了咖啡。在您能够击败一台巨大的打字机之前，您需要一把武器。在战场上建造工厂并处理材料来制作武器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >连接工厂</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/acbfa2301d0d06a599711481b3aeba40.avif?t=1771047675\" width=600 height=210 /></span><br>使用USB供电的传送带将工厂连接起来，制造出数十种不同战斗风格的武器。投掷不明飞行物射出一阵子弹。建造一个啃机器人冲向敌人，或使用D20骰子达到爆炸性的效果。罗波弗伦兹的多武器，劈砍战斗系统易于学习，但具有策略深度。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造机器</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/2166254a2d2a5b9027ff77af975fc87e.poster.avif?t=1771047675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/2166254a2d2a5b9027ff77af975fc87e.webm?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/2166254a2d2a5b9027ff77af975fc87e.mp4?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>建造一门大炮并使用制造的武器作为弹药，或建造一个弹簧缓冲器来击退狂暴的机器人。制作数十种由物理驱动的机器，并将它们与您制造的武器结合，拥有无尽的可能性。您甚至可以通过在战场上建立相互连接的工厂和机器来自动化您的战斗！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设您的城镇</h2>利用制造的力量定制欧米兰，您自己的建设中心世界。通过连接机器和工厂解决难题，解锁新的武器用于战斗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/9af9bcc1866db916f569412c248706fa.poster.avif?t=1771047675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/9af9bcc1866db916f569412c248706fa.webm?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324550/extras/9af9bcc1866db916f569412c248706fa.mp4?t=1771047675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>单独挑战暴躁的游戏机，或在双人合作模式中与朋友一起建造机器迷宫。",
